This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep neural networks and their training, which are topics commonly associated with machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions video coloring and optical flow estimation, which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
